@DN
Lay out the meat and broil it. It’s definitely the way I have always made this at home. The rolled-up parchment sounds unappetizing, and it won’t have any crispy bits. Sounds like you’re just going to make a pile of mush meat! 
Add homemade tzatziki or the white sauce, which is my favorite. It’s yogurt and mayo mixed.

